==Starting off==
* '''Player:''' Good day King Lathas.
* '''King Lathas:''' And to you adventurer. I assume you're here about King Tyras?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I am. What's our plan?}}
** '''Player:''' I am. What's our plan?
** '''King Lathas:''' Well, as we've previously discussed, my brother is currently gathering strength in the lands west of here. The only known way into those lands is through the Underground Pass.
** '''King Lathas:''' Unfortunately, the pass is a treacherous place. Some of my best soldiers have fallen trying to find a way though.
** '''King Lathas:''' To make matters worse, some crazed group of cultists has recently made their home in the pass. Their leader, some madman named Iban, claims to be the son of Zamorak himself.
** '''Player:''' Well that doesn't sound good. So what do you need from me?
** '''King Lathas:''' If my brother is to be stopped, a way through the Underground Pass must be found. This is the task I have for you. Do you think you're up for it?
** {{tselect|Start the Underground Pass quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' There's only one way to find out. Where do I start?
*** '''King Lathas:''' You'll find the entrance to the Underground Pass at the far end of West Ardougne. My main tracker, Koftik, will meet you there.
*** '''King Lathas:''' Together, you are to find a way through the pass. Once you have done so, return to me.
*** '''Player:''' I'll do my best.
*** '''King Lathas:''' Remember, the Underground Pass is lethal. Go prepared with food and armour or you won't last long.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' It sounds too dangerous for me. I'd better prepare more first.
*** '''King Lathas:''' Very well. Return to me when you are ready.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I'm just passing through.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm just passing through.
** '''King Lathas:''' Fair enough. Return to me when you are ready and we will discuss our next steps.
** {{tact|end}}

